Introduction

Jae Chan is a South Korean singer-songwriter, composer, and actor under Dongyo Entertainment. He is a member of boy group DKZ and its first sub-unit DONGKIZ I:KAN. He has also starred in web dramas such as "Youtuber Class" and "Semantic Error."

Jaechan debuted as a member of DONGKIZ on April 24, 2019 with their first single album "DONGKIZ On The Block."
